commit 6bae95035db026b7f3189a21942ce7953a6e3437
Author: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>
Date:   Tue Oct 6 12:07:45 2009 +1000

    Require macros 1.3 for XORG_DEFAULT_OPTIONS
    
